Css Position values 
1 Static
2 Relative
3 Absolute
4 Fixed
5 Sticky (not work on all broswers)

Helper properties

(left, right) you can only use one
(top, bottom) you can only use one

.con4{
            border-radius: 5px;
            border:1px solid limegreen;
            height: 200px;
            width: 200px;
            position: absolute;
            top:200px;
            left: 500px;
            animation-name: con1;
            animation-duration: 5s;
        }

        @keyframes con1 {
            0% {
                background-color: lightcoral;
                left: 0px;
                top: 0px;
            }

            25% {
                background-color: yellow;
                left: 200px;
                top: 0px;
            }

            50% {
                background-color: blue;
                left: 200px;
                top: 200px;
            }

            75% {
                background-color: green;
                left: 0px;
                top: 200px;
            }

            100% {
                background-color: red;
                left: 0px;
                top: 0px;
            }
        }
